// === Adjectives ===

// --- First and Second Declensions ---
// Large (masculine, singular): magnus magni magno magnum magno
// Large (masculine, plural): magni magnorum magnis magnos magnis
// Large (feminine, singular): magna magnae magnae magnam magna
// Large (feminine, plural): magnae magnarum magnis magnas magnis
// Large (neuter, singular): magnum magni magno magnum magno
// Large (neuter, plural): magna magnorum magnis magna magnis

// Free (masculine, singular): liber liberi libero liberum libero
// Free (feminine, singular): libera liberae liberae liberam libera
// Free (neuter, singular): liberum liberi libero liberum libero

// Beautiful (masculine, singular): pulcher pulchri pulchro pulchrum pulchro
// Beautiful (feminine, singular): pulchra pulchrae pulchrae pulchram pulchra
// Beautiful (neuter, singular): pulchrum pulchri pulchro pulchrum pulchro

// --- Third Declension ---
// [Two endings]
// Brave (masculine, singular): fortis fortis forti fortem forti
// Brave (masculine, plural): fortes fortium fortibus fortes fortibus
// Brave (feminine, singular): fortis fortis forti fortem forti
// Brave (feminine, plural): fortes fortium fortibus fortes fortibus
// Brave (neuter, singular): forte fortis forti forte forti
// Brave (neuter, plural): fortia fortium fortibus fortia fortibus

// [Three endings]
// Keen (masculine, singular): acer acris acri acrem acri
// Keen (masculine, plural): acres acrium acribus acres acribus
// Keen (feminine, singular): acris acris acri acrem acri
// Keen (feminine, plural): acres acrium acribus acres acribus
// Keen (neuter, singular): acre acris acri acre acri
// Keen (neuter, plural): acria acrium acribus acria acribus

// [One ending]
// Powerful (masculine, singular): potens potentis potenti potentem potenti
// Powerful (masculine, plural): potentes potentium potentibus potentes potentibus
// Powerful (feminine, singular): potens potentis potenti potentem potenti
// Powerful (feminine, plural): potentes potentium potentibus potentes potentibus
// Powerful (neuter, singular): potens potentis potenti potens potenti
// Powerful (neuter, plural): potentia potentium potentibus potentia potentibus

// [Comparatives]
// Braver (masculine, singular): fortior fortioris fortiori fortiorem fortiore
